- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper deals with processing and analyzing large-scale trajectory data. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper discusses the implications of analyzing urban trajectories on society. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper may touch upon privacy concerns related to analyzing trajectory data.
